<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa6">
<l>puḷḷum cilampiṉa kāṇ puḷḷaraiyaṉ kōyilil</l>
<l>veḷḷai viḷi caṅkiṉ pēraravam kēṭṭilaiyō</l>
<l>piḷḷāy eḻuntirāy pēy mulai nañcuṇṭu</l>
<l>kaḷḷac cakaṭam kalakkaḻiyak kālōcci</l>
<l>veḷḷattaravil tuyilamarnta vittiṉai</l>
<l>uḷḷattuk koṇṭu muṉivarkaḷum yōkikaḷum</l>
<l>meḷḷa veḻuntari eṉṟa pēraravam</l>
<l>uḷḷam pukuntu kuḷirntēlōr empāvāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, the birds too have [started to] chirp!</l>
<l>Have you not heard the great sound of the white summoning conch</l>
<l rend="indent">at the temple of the lord of the birds (Garuḍa)?</l>
<l>O girl, do get up!</l>
<l>The great sound of the hermits and the ascetics saying ‘Hari’</l>
<l rend="indent">—getting up slowly,</l>
<l rend="indent">keeping in [their] hearts</l>
<l rend="indent">the Cause that remained asleep on the snake upon the sea waves,</l>
<l rend="indent">having thrust [His] feet into the fake cart so that [its] joints were destroyed,</l>
<l rend="indent">and eaten poison from the demoness’s breasts—</l>
<l>enters [our] hearts [and] cools [it].</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
